        Parameters:
        actionEvent -
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - RUNTIME ERROR - After initially creating the AddProduct.fxml file and trying to load the controller, I was receiving a java.lang.ClassNotFoundException and the controller would not load. Looking at the cause breakpoint, I determined that the fx:controller was incorrectly named. After changing it to match the .fxml file name, the controller loaded without issue.
